<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to Shopa</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background-color: #2E7D32; padding: 40px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #FDC500; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -1px; }
    .header p { color: #ffffff; margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; }
    .body { padding: 40px 32px; }
    .body h2 { color: #151515; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .body p { color: #555555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #2E7D32; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 8px 0 24px; }
    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea; margin: 24px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 24px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #9b9b9b; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Shopa</h1>
      <p>Your campus marketplace</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Welcome to Shopa, {{firstName}}! 🎉</h2>
      <p>You're now part of the largest campus marketplace in Nigeria. Discover amazing products from student vendors right on your campus.</p>
      <p>Here's what you can do on Shopa:</p>
      <p>🛒 <strong>Shop</strong> — Browse products from verified student vendors on your campus</p>
      <p>💳 <strong>Pay securely</strong> — All payments are protected with escrow until you confirm delivery</p>
      <p>⭐ <strong>Review</strong> — Rate vendors and products to help your fellow students</p>
      <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/home" class="btn">Start Shopping</a>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9b9b9b;">If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} Shopa. All rights reserved.<br/>Crawford University Campus Marketplace</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
